		<abstract>
			<para>This document is intended for software developers interested
				in developing applications that use the Rackspace
				Cloud Identity Service, which is an implementation of
				OpenStack's Keystone Identity Service for identity
				authentication, authorization, and service
				administration. This document also includes details on
				how to integrate services with the Rackspace Cloud
				Identity Service.</para>
		</abstract>
